title: Sister Wendy, My Favorite Things-75 Works of Art
description:
Sister Wendy, My Favorite Things: 75 Works of Art from Around the World
Harry N. Abrams | 1999 | 0810943875 | English | 168 pages | PDF | 20 MB

The 75 artworks Sister Wendy showcases here are among the ones that have intrigued and impressed her the most over the years. As well as popular works by Michaelangelo and van Gogh, less well known pieces, such as a Chinese painting and a chess piece, are featured
